imageDescription: A person standing defiantly in front of a group of people, arms crossed and head held high. The person is wearing torn and dirty clothes, and their hair is messy. The people in the background are all reaching out to them, some with pleading expressions and others with angry ones. The person in the foreground remains unyielding, their eyes filled with determination.
